Subject: Works great with one MAJOR flaw!
Body: WPP is great, but there's a major flaw that will make it unusable for most people. I'm still on 4.3, but I think this may be the problem others are complaining about without understanding it. WPP will not allow you to load the authentication page necessary to connect to many open networks, e.g. Starbucks, and you are instantly kicked off as a result. That goes EVEN for networks that are already explicitly allowed and on WPP's hot spot list. The ONLY way to connect to such networks is to force close the app.

Subject: One major flaw
Body: Although this app keeps you from logging on to wi-fi spoofs, it also keeps you from logging on to wi-fi sources that you are actually trying to log on to  You try, it doesn't work, and then you have to find the screen .that allows you to permit the same wi-fi.
